U.K. Foreign Office Investigates Abduction of Briton in Nigeria

-- B y   P a t r i c i a   K u o
-- 
2011-05-14T12:21:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-14/u-k-foreign-office-investigates-abduction-of-briton-in-nigeria.html
The Foreign Office said it is
investigating reports about the abduction of a British national
in  Nigeria .  Gunmen seized two foreigners, a British national and an
Italian, in the northern town of Birnin Kebbi yesterday,
according to  Hassan Ahmed , police commissioner for Kebbi state.
The police are making efforts to track the abductors, he said.  “We are aware of reports of a missing British national. We
are urgently looking into the reports,” a Foreign Office
spokeswoman said by e-mail today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Patricia Kuo in London at 
 pkuo2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
